title: Gnuteq: The Cutting Edge Of Everything All The Time
description:
Gnuteq is a multidimensional manufacturer of solutions. We have a wide spectrum in regards to our industrial participation that expands across a myriad of arenas. Those arenas include both products and services .
We do not intend to brand a specific product or service with the creation of this logo, but rather we look to brand our approach. Our stance is that we are always at the forefront of innovation in regards to all of our endeavors. We occupy the space in between what has been done(the knowable) and what has not been done(the unknowable); a space we like to reference as the cutting edge of perception.
Received knowledge belongs within the realm of the visible. The Gnu(new) scientists stand at the edge of this knowledge and gaze into the expanse of the unknowable.
The task is not to enlighten the world, but to push against the boundariesto enlarge the knowledge.
The invisible world extends beyond what we can consider to be the microcosm and macrocosm. It stretches back into a timeless past.
Where chaos begins, classical science stops.
For the most part, we already know what we want the image to look like. This is merely a formality to bring our own signature rendition to life. Essentially what we want is a downward facing tetrahedron like the one posted in the photo with the light blue background. What weve done is taken and framed the top corner of a cube hence the term cutting edge. That is precisely the exact thing that we want. Ive sent other photos to amplify and reinforce the overall message which is that we are always at the cutting edge of perception.
other_notes:
We only want the slogan included if it can be done tastefully. For us, simplicity is king. We want the image to speak louder than what any words can convey.
Imagine that this will be a breast pocket logo.
I CANNOT STRESS ENOUGH THAT THE IMAGE THAT IS MOST TO MY LIKING IS THE WHITE TETRAHEDRAL IMAGE WITH THE BLUE BACKGROUND. WE'D PREFER IF IT HAD A 3 DIMENSIONAL FEEL TO IT. IT IS LITERALLY THE EDGE OF A HEXAGON/CUBE. IT IS EITHER AN INNER CORNER OR AN OUTER CORNER, BUT A CORNER NONETHELESS. THE MESSAGE TO ADHERE TO IS CUTTING EDGE. "A CHIP OFF THE OLD BLOCK." I WANT TO TO BE ABLE TO EXPERIENCE THAT IN THE IMAGE PLEASE. THANK YOU.
